example:
AWS IAM Politikası ile MFA Zorlama (koşullu erişim):
  {
    "Version":"2012-10-17",
    "Statement":[{
      "Effect":"Deny",
      "Action":"*",
      "Resource":"*",
      "Condition":{"Bool":{"aws:MultiFactorAuthPresent":"false"}}
    }]
  }

AWS IAM MFA Koşulu:
  {
    "Statement":[{
      "Effect":"Deny",
      "Action":"iam:*",
      "Resource":"*",
      "Condition":{"Bool":{"aws:MultiFactorAuthPresent":"false"}}
    }]
  }

AWS Trust Policy (rolü assume edebilecek varlık):
{
  "Version":"2012-10-17",
  "Statement":[{
    "Effect":"Allow",
    "Principal":{"AWS":"arn:aws:iam::123456789012:user/deploy"},
    "Action":"sts:AssumeRole"
  }]
}

S3 Lifecycle Kuralı (JSON):
{
  "Rules":[{
    "ID":"LogsToGlacier",
    "Filter":{"Prefix":"logs/"},
    "Status":"Enabled",
    "Transitions":[{"Days":30,"StorageClass":"GLACIER"}],
    "Expiration":{"Days":365}
  }] 
}

S3 Bucket Policy (VPCe koşulu):
{
  "Version":"2012-10-17",
  "Statement":[{
    "Effect":"Allow",
    "Principal":"*",
    "Action":"s3:GetObject",
    "Resource":"arn:aws:s3:::ornek-bucket/*",
    "Condition":{"StringEquals":{"aws:SourceVpce":"vpce-abc123"}}
  }]
}

İmzalı URL Policy (örnek):
{
  "Statement":[{
    "Resource":"https://d111.cloudfront.net/private/*",
    "Condition":{"DateLessThan":{"AWS:EpochTime":1893456000}}
  }]
}

AWS State Machine (özet):
{
  "StartAt":"Process",
  "States":{
    "Process":{"Type":"Task","Resource":"arn:aws:lambda:eu-west-1:123:function:proc","Catch":[{"ErrorEquals":["States.ALL"],"Next":"Fallback"}],"Next":"Done"},
    "Fallback":{"Type":"Pass","Result":"retry","Next":"Done"},
    "Done":{"Type":"Succeed"}
  }
}

AWS IAM ABAC Politikası (tag koşulu):
{
  "Version":"2012-10-17",
  "Statement":[{
    "Effect":"Allow",
    "Action":"ec2:*",
    "Resource":"*",
    "Condition":{"StringEquals":{"aws:ResourceTag/Project":"X","aws:PrincipalTag/Project":"X"}}
  }]
}
Azure RBAC Atama:
az role assignment create --assignee <principalId> --role "Reader" --scope /subscriptions/<sub>/resourceGroups/rg
